    "en": "**Smoked Rosemary Gimlet**\n\nA modern twist on the classic Gimlet, featuring:\n*   Smoked rosemary for an aromatic and smoky note\n*   Fresh lime juice for tartness\n*   Simple syrup for sweetness",
